Name: Software
Description: The name of the file format, or the software package that works with the file.

Name: IsCompressed
Description: Indicates whether the file format is compressed.

Name: DropVariables
Description: A list of names of variables that will be dropped during the save operation.

Name: KeepVariables
Description: A list of names of variables that will be kept during the save operation. All other variables will be dropped.

Name: RenameVariables
Description: A list of variables that will be renamed as part of the save operation.
